column17:
Elizabeth Taylor White Diamonds Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.2765

White Diamonds from the celebrated classic brand of Elizabeth Taylor is one for the woman who enjoys all things exquisite elegant and delectable. This vintage perfume is one of the most popular celebrity launches that appeared in 1991 and was the inspiration for a host of other celebrity perfumes in the years to come. A classic in its own right the golden elixir appears in a slender studded glass flacon and titillates with its glamorous sensuality and erotic appeal. Dominantly floral in its assortment of aromas the first whiff of this enigmatic fluid suggests hints of Aldehydes Orange Lily Neroli and Bergamot. This gradually fades into the more pronounced and intense notes of Italian Orris Root Carnation Cinnamon Egyptian Tuberose Jasmine Turkish Rose Ylang Ylang and Narcissus. The base notes of this scintillating scent comprise Amber Patchouli Musk Oakmoss and Sandalwood that leave you feeling vivacious and beautiful. As priceless as the precious stone the Elizabeth Taylor White Diamonds Eau de Toilette justifies its claim as a classic bestseller.
